caption: Please know what you’re ordering when placing an order here. Spare ribs are listed on the menu but you may get spare rib tips if you don’t know what the person in this establishment means by short bone or long bone. Yes!!! Short bone is spare rib ribs. No don’t say duh.. My other Chinese menus actually say Spare rib tips. They didn’t even offer to change my order or maybe next time you order “ Hey here’s a soda”. But whatever I know next time!
